Privacy Policy
By using Simple Interval Timer you accept this privacy policy.
Apple HealthKit Integration
While used on Apple Watch, Simple Interval Timer will track your heart rate, display it in the watch app, and write the heart rate data to the Apple HealthKit database at your specific request.
Simple Interval Timer cannot read or write data from nor to the Apple HealthKit database unless you specifically grant access.
This data is neither stored within the Simple Interval timer app itself, nor transmitted anywhere by the Simple Interval Timer app.
Simple Interval Timer is in no way responsible for the protection of data and information stored within the Apple HealthKit database. It is strongly recommended that you review Appleâ€™s applicable policies and procedures before synching and backup up your Apple HealthKit data.
